data.description: The Lance is a Beautiful Open Floor plan featuring 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath and Bonus located in Hardin Valley,  the Fastest growing area of Knox County!! This home has ALL the features you are looking for: Hardwoods, Granite, Stainless Steel appliances, Tile Shower and more...Most Importantly this Gorgeous home and its Quality features is Built by Local Builder Vertical Constructors where Attention to Detail is Top Priority!! UNDER CONSTRUCTION, ESTIMATED COMPLETION JULY 2018!!
data.whatILove: I love the open floor plan, upgraded features that are standard for this local builder who's attention to detail is impeccable. Large master suite with Tile Walk in Shower (this is not your typical Master Bath), GREAT location in a quaint neighborhood.
